  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow"><img src="/media/1722/italy_livigno_snowboarder.jpg" alt="Free Local Area Lift Pass for departures on 16th December 2017" rel="840,401" /></div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>Receive a Free Local Area Lift Pass when you travel to <strong>Livigno</strong>, departing <strong>16<sup>th</sup> December 2017</strong> for 7 nights!</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e469a37cba1c498e9197c6963def7b89}" title="Livigno"><strong>Livigno</strong></a>, is known for its excellent snow record, long winter season, duty-free status and tremendous value.</p>
<p>New to our Winter 2017/18 programme and lying close to the Swiss border, it has a modern lift network village charm and a wealth of winter entertainment. The 115km of pistes, split across the two sides of the valley and efficiently linked by the free resort bus network.</p>
<p>Take advantage of this fantastic offer today and make the most of your free lift pass.</p>
</div>
<div> </div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Applies to new bookings made from 1st July 2017, for departures on 16th December 2017.</li>
<li>Applies to area lift passes only.</li>
<li>The offer is valid while stocks last, may be withdrawn at anytime.</li>
<li>Applies to all properties we feature in Livigno.</li>
<li>All prices, offers and availability are correct at time of publishing, are subject to change &amp; availability and can be withdrawn at anytime.</li>
<li>All offers are for 7 nights unless otherwise stated.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>]]></bodyText>
